00:22:32.618 --> 00:22:34.953 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to see my
doctor more often."

00:22:34.953 --> 00:22:38.056 align:middle line:84%
Plus they have the doctor's
have tremendous amount more

00:22:38.056 --> 00:22:43.095 align:middle line:84%
at their disposal to identify
your disease before it happens.

00:22:43.095 --> 00:22:46.198 align:middle line:84%
You know, I don't
know how many George

00:22:46.198 --> 00:22:48.934 align:middle line:84%
and I were doing
this show together

00:22:48.934 --> 00:22:52.271 align:middle line:90%
