00:23:01.914 --> 00:23:02.781 align:middle line:90%
You remember that?

00:23:02.781 --> 00:23:03.882 align:middle line:84%
>> George Noory:
I remember that.

00:23:03.882 --> 00:23:05.250 align:middle line:84%
>> Christian Wilde:
And he confirmed that.

00:23:05.250 --> 00:23:06.919 align:middle line:84%
And now there's an
article last week

00:23:06.919 --> 00:23:09.087 align:middle line:84%
about how many surgeons
die very early

00:23:09.087 --> 00:23:11.924 align:middle line:84%
through the stress
they're under.

00:23:11.924 --> 00:23:14.927 align:middle line:84%
So I know we get very
