You have to check your vitamin
D. They didn't know that until

00:25:19.218 --> 00:25:20.652 align:middle line:90%
about three years ago.

00:25:20.652 --> 00:25:24.456 align:middle line:84%
>> George Noory: It is senseless
not to take care of yourself.

00:25:24.456 --> 00:25:25.757 align:middle line:84%
>> Christian Wilde:
It really is.

00:25:25.757 --> 00:25:27.559 align:middle line:84%
>> George Noory:
When it is so easy.

