unless you were checked.

00:26:20.812 --> 00:26:23.882 align:middle line:84%
If you're taking a
drug called Tricor,

00:26:23.882 --> 00:26:26.251 align:middle line:90%
a fibrate drug or Gemfibrozil.

00:26:26.251 --> 00:26:29.621 align:middle line:84%
It will raise your homocysteine
levels to danger levels.

00:26:29.621 --> 00:26:31.623 align:middle line:90%
50 percent higher.

00:26:31.623 --> 00:26:34.026 align:middle line:84%
So, knowing your
homocysteine is another one

00:26:34.026 --> 00:26:36.461 align:middle line:84%
of those tests I talk
about in the books.

00:26:36.461 --> 00:26:38.030 align:middle line:90%
I lay them out for you.

00:26:38.030 --> 00:26:40.766 align:middle line:84%
Ask for these tests,
I insist on them.

00:26:40.766 --> 00:26:43.969 align:middle line:84%
Now doctors are doing
it more often.

00:26:43.969 --> 00:26:46.738 align:middle line:84%
>> George Noory: And of course
there's my favorite spice.

00:26:46.738 --> 00:26:47.572 align:middle line:90%
Turmeric.

