They became depressed.

00:50:02.699 --> 00:50:08.939 align:middle line:84%
Your body requires cholesterol
to produce [inaudible]

00:50:08.939 --> 00:50:12.709 align:middle line:90%
if you lower it too much,

00:50:12.709 --> 00:50:17.648 align:middle line:84%
the brain which is effected
very definitely by cholesterol.

00:50:17.648 --> 00:50:20.784 align:middle line:84%
When you lower it too much,
the protective membrane

00:50:20.784 --> 00:50:22.653 align:middle line:90%
that keeps you from bleeding,

00:50:22.653 --> 00:50:26.657 align:middle line:84%
having brain bleeds,
is suddenly weakened.

00:50:26.657 --> 00:50:29.593 align:middle line:84%
And you can have a
hemorrhagic stroke.

00:50:29.593 --> 00:50:33.030 align:middle line:84%
I'm not saying everybody
who's cholesterol is 115,

00:50:33.030 --> 00:50:34.164 align:middle line:90%
that's going to happen.

00:50:34.164 --> 00:50:37.367 align:middle line:84%
But the possibility is
that it could happen.

00:50:37.367 --> 00:50:38.936 align:middle line:90%
Here is the point.

00:50:38.936 --> 00:50:42.473 align:middle line:84%
Cholesterol is not
your big enemy.

00:50:42.473 --> 00:50:45.542 align:middle line:90%
It is LDM cholesterol.

00:50:45.542 --> 00:50:47.678 align:middle line:90%
